# --- Trouble Tickets ---
<https://w3id.org/noria/troubleticket/DBOutage_TT001>
    a noria:TroubleTicket ;
    rdfs:label "E-commerce Database Outage"@en, "Panne Base de Données E-commerce"@fr ;
    rdfs:comment "Critical incident: E-commerce database server is unreachable, impacting customer services."@en ;
